In 2015 CARS established a CRANE Network (Competition and Regulation. Academic Network. Europe – Visegrad, Balkan, Baltic, East) consisting of research units and academics from Central and Eastern Europe focused on competition policy and sector specific regulation. CARS as research unit and most of CARS members are members of CRANE.  &#xd;
